      "value": "<p><strong>Scroll of Inflict Wounds</strong> (Level 1 Necromancy)</p><p>Make a melee spell attack against a creature you can reach. On a hit, the target takes 3d10 necrotic damage.</p><p><em>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 2nd level or higher, the damage increases by 1d10 for each slot level above 1st.</em></p><p><strong>Components:</strong> V, S</p><p><strong>Casting Time:</strong> 1 action | <strong>Range:</strong> Touch | <strong>Duration:</strong> Instantaneous</p><p><em>Classes: Cleric</em></p>",
